This directory contains Arduino sketches for use with NodeMCU Sensor Shield v1 from BurgessWorld Custom Electroics tindie store
https://tindie.com/stores/cburgess129

Sketch NodeMCU_Sensor_Shield_CORE_V1.ino gets loaded onto the NodeMCU Sensor Board
This requires the use of a USB-Serial Adapter.
NOTE:  This sketch comes pre-loaded on the Sensor Board when shipped

